Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.05,0:01:24.60,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛が愛を「重過ぎる」って理解を拒み
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.77,0:01:29.40,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎しみに　変わって行く前に…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.54,0:01:31.37,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもそうだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.49,0:01:36.39,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,バツの悪い事情にはいつも蓋して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.50,0:01:39.22,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食わせ物のリアル
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.33,0:01:41.55,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歪んだジレンマ時代で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:45.31,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束したはずの二人さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.45,0:01:49.79,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,気付かず通り過ぎて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:01:57.41,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壊しあって　解り合ったことも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.59,0:01:59.22,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,置き去りにした
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.34,0:02:02.66,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,これが成れの果てなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.79,0:02:07.20,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認めないで　立ち向かったときも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.81,0:02:13.41,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落ちて行く時のイメージから逃げ出せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.55,0:02:18.15,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah　何度でも探し出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.25,0:02:24.90,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君の目　その手の温もりを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:30.24,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛はいつも私を傷つけるだけ…って君はつぶやいて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.35,0:02:34.90,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信じる事が怖くて泣いたんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.09,0:02:37.15,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱さを知って強くなれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:40.91,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐れず信じることで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.03,0:02:45.93,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本当の愛を知るだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.05,0:01:24.60,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱说爱「过于沉重」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.77,0:01:29.40,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在转变成恨之前　把它拒绝于心门之外…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.54,0:01:31.37,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万物皆是如此吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.49,0:01:36.39,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是把不合时宜的事隐藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.50,0:01:39.22,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是冒牌货的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.33,0:01:41.55,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在扭曲了的窘迫时代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:45.31,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连本应定下约定的两人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.45,0:01:49.79,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都会毫无察觉地擦肩而过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:01:57.41,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那开始崩坏但曾经互相理解的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.59,0:01:59.22,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将其撇下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.34,0:02:02.66,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓的末路吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.79,0:02:07.20,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中不服　想与之对抗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.81,0:02:13.41,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要从当初堕落的印象中逃离开去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.55,0:02:18.15,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　就算历经千百次也要找出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.25,0:02:24.90,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的双眸　你手中的余温
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:30.24,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小声嘟囔着「爱总是让我遍体鳞伤…」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.35,0:02:34.90,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因畏惧坚信不疑的事而哭过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.09,0:02:37.15,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道软弱才能变强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:40.91,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要害怕坚信不疑地走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.03,0:02:45.93,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是爱的真谛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.09,0:02:57.12,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}#09 无法逝去的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.71,0:00:04.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  是我的失误
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.02,0:00:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.20,0:00:07.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到了  刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.04,0:00:10.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界的扭曲点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.86,0:00:12.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  我们要用Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.45,0:00:15.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将世界的扭曲破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.21,0:00:16.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.16,0:00:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.13,0:00:22.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throne的发展型？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.13,0:00:22.75,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Arche Gundam：权天使高达，Throne系列的发展型）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.34,0:00:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难…难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.67,0:00:28.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  这就开战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.06,0:00:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam之间盛大的战争！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.25,0:00:35.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧  Fang
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.90,0:00:41.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.05,0:00:43.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与以前大不相同了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:54.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不来劲啊  Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.30,0:01:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还活着吗  阿里·阿尔·沙谢斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.81,0:01:05.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  但拜你们所赐  半个肩膀烧焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.61,0:01:08.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙的命还远远不够呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.34,0:01:12.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.68,0:01:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要拿你的性命来为再生治疗付账！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.12,0:02:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OO和Seravee处于战斗状态
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.39,0:03:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然被A-LAWS盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.73,0:03:04.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派Gundam过去果然没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.93,0:03:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联系待机中的阿里路亚他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.04,0:03:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧  克鲁吉斯的小鬼 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.94,0:03:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克恩的仇人就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.63,0:03:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来为他报一箭之仇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.43,0:03:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.21,0:03:44.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右眼看不见还跑到战场上作战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.55,0:03:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐藏手臂…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲开了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.86,0:03:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边也有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.69,0:04:07.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特瑞亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:10.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:17.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fang
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.71,0:04:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起升天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:29.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援军？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.78,0:04:32.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四对一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.31,0:04:38.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形势十分不利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:47.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  特瑞亚  皇小姐发来了归舰命令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.59,0:04:49.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特瑞亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么制止我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.69,0:04:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是洛克恩的仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.22,0:04:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥的…仇人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.09,0:05:03.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还活着…阿里·阿尔·沙谢斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.58,0:05:08.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克鲁吉斯的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:10.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个倔强的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.36,0:05:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  必须这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样才有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李杰尼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.21,0:05:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜你所赐派对搞得一团糟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.15,0:05:33.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惹怒特瑞亚·埃德的可是你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.09,0:05:37.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好劝的话  本可能把他拉到我们阵营的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏得我事先做了这么多准备
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.17,0:05:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望他们与我们对抗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:49.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being活动得越频繁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS就越会遵照舆论的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:54.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行动也就变得顺理成章
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.57,0:05:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.17,0:05:58.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区一个卡塔隆太不过瘾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:06:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为战斗用而出生的我就没出场机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.04,0:06:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Twin-Drive系统
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭载了两个GN Drive的Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.36,0:06:15.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是Celestial Being独立开发的产品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:21.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是与TRANS-AM系统一样  同属伊奥利亚·修亨伯格的遗产
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.46,0:06:22.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪个都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:27.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像那种性能  远比不上Gadessa
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:27.04,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Gadessa：GNZ-003  改革者开发的机体  机师为李维夫·李拜巴尔）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.81,0:06:31.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次战斗中李维夫·李拜巴尔会证明的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要准备让我出场啊  李本兹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.19,0:06:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那他们安然逃离了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:54.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与改革者的对立  会促使变革的加速
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:57.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很期待会如何发展呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.57,0:07:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准尉  感觉怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.79,0:07:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.75,0:07:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳您费心了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.15,0:07:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于我的身体  你没有听说什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.19,0:07:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让我打听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.02,0:07:23.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…十分感谢体谅我的难处
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.80,0:07:27.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到部队会展开追击Gundam作战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:29.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:30.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝·哈莱维
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.15,0:07:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4年前由于Gundam的攻击失去了所有亲人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自身也遭受到毒性GN粒子的辐射
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:47.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,细胞受到损害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.52,0:07:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是复仇吗？  如此年轻就踏上战场的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.03,0:08:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个与华丽的礼服如此相配的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.99,0:08:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个少年是Celestial Being的成员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:12.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那·F·清荣…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:18.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架机体…MR.武士道！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.42,0:08:24.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam各机收容完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.53,0:08:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始全部GN Drive对托勒密的对接
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回宇宙？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据我的推测  12小时以内敌人会展开包围网式的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.21,0:08:38.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是逃不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.73,0:08:40.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  回到拉格朗日3
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能修补Gundam以及得到支援机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.74,0:08:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特  米蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:50.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能开始脱离大气层的程序么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:51.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到路易丝了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.56,0:08:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很偶然的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:01.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:05.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  还打听了一些你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.99,0:09:07.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉她你在宇宙工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:10.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没和她联系过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.18,0:09:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架Gundam是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.84,0:09:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有哥哥的仇人又是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.68,0:09:23.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如我所说的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.51,0:09:28.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶那架Gundam的阿里·阿尔·沙谢斯夺走了洛克恩的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:30.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里·阿尔·沙谢斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:33.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请说的更详细些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.23,0:09:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯密尔诺夫少尉  哈莱维准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.39,0:09:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全返回
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.99,0:09:44.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:52.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据失去Gundam的地点  经过时间以及移动速度计算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.27,0:09:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推测出敌舰会航行于这片区域
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.48,0:10:00.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我队会派出6架Trilobite包围整个区域
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:03.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦发现敌舰立刻进行攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制空权确保了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.80,0:10:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派2个MS小队足够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.11,0:10:12.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们该不会直接从海里钻出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.32,0:10:15.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望把战术与以往的例子相关联
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:17.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.15,0:10:21.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌舰曾突破了大气层  降落到地面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么反过来也行有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.94,0:10:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.09,0:10:27.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的想法也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam的GN Drive有个名叫TRANS-AM的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.97,0:10:34.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高浓度粒子全面解放的系统
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用这一技术恐怕就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:41.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建议与部署在同步卫星轨道上的部队配合
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:47.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方的作战指挥官也看穿了刚刚的正规战术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.80,0:10:50.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是无礼  你想愚弄身为长官的我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:52.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我获得了许可
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.93,0:10:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.76,0:10:56.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是One-man Amry吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:10:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与Mr.武士道不同 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.02,0:11:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保证会遵照上校的指示行事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.56,0:11:05.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是令人欣慰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.41,0:11:09.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.97,0:11:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥为了帮家人复仇盯上了沙谢斯那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.11,0:11:15.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在笑什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.59,0:11:19.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私仇比改变世界都重要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.47,0:11:20.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真像哥哥的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:22.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不满吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.09,0:11:25.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我很尊敬他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:28.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人都死了10多年了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不可能纠结这么久
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:35.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算仇人就在眼前吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.95,0:11:40.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾隶属于KBSA  那个夺去你家人生命的组织
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.59,0:11:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:51.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用做到这个程度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是必须说的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.79,0:11:58.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的  我要代替神完成未尽的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:11:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.92,0:12:02.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  你居然怕死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.44,0:12:04.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是亵渎神灵的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:10.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场战争是奉献给神的一次圣战
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对蔑视传统  毁坏着神的土地的非信仰者们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.49,0:12:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为神的代言人  我们将挥下制裁的铁锤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.87,0:12:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那时候  我劝阻了同伴的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.86,0:12:36.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克恩  不  尼尔·迪兰地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就不会成为Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.16,0:12:44.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你能劝得了一时  恐怖袭击终究还是会发生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.47,0:12:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事是躲不过的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.58,0:12:48.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.92,0:12:50.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是过去的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.94,0:12:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后悔过去也无济于事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:57.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  我们不是为了过去  而是为了未来而战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.58,0:13:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵照自己坚信的正义而活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:13.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这真的与未来相连吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.49,0:13:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与改革者敌对…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.16,0:13:18.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有真正的未来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,================================================
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:31.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是在开发新型机
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:36.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉…不  现在是叫Mr.武士道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人擅自这么叫的  实在麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.87,0:13:42.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你挺喜欢这名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  今天有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.71,0:13:48.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来祝贺你就任开发主任
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.90,0:13:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.56,0:13:55.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  希望你把那台还在试作阶段的机体交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.01,0:13:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来这才是你来的目的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对它有什么要求吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最快的速度和最强的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.41,0:14:08.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.96,0:14:14.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为交换  你一定要将Celestial Being解决掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.74,0:14:18.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然  我只是为此而活着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.69,0:14:25.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  现在你所属的部队不是正在作战中吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.75,0:14:27.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对舰队战没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.91,0:14:29.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都将作战内容看得如此透彻了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:32.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锻炼过洞察力了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.65,0:14:42.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS队全体出击  Trilobite各机已到达索敌区域
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.37,0:14:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  在发现敌舰的同时开始作战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.58,0:14:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望您明白我跟本次作战毫无关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:53.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你的便
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.23,0:14:58.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会加油的  上校
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是Gadessa
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:07.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是新型机吗  A-LAWS到底接受了多少捐款
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.77,0:15:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  Celestial Being将如何应对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.42,0:15:22.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还没向皇·李·诺瑞加报告吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.74,0:15:27.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在整理头绪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:30.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我之前的下文吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:32.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找到的扭曲点是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.55,0:15:35.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:44.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变革总是伴有伤痛  你们不也是这么过来的么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要管别的  自己去做不就得了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是为计划而生的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.52,0:15:54.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是被伊奥里亚那个老爷子托付了Gundam的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.32,0:15:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们已经成了伊奥里亚的计划的障碍了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.59,0:15:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:02.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认到6台敌人的水中用MA
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:05.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请各位到指定位置就位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.12,0:16:07.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.31,0:16:07.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.47,0:16:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人包围住托勒密并逐渐接近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:13.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预计他们开始攻击的时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.31,0:16:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0024
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.61,0:16:19.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人预测到我们在赤道上了…真有一手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.41,0:16:22.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.85,0:16:25.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐到辅助席上去吧  晃动会很大的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.55,0:16:27.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.47,0:16:32.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密  采取急速上浮姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.45,0:16:42.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从中东湾直接飞进宇宙  以逃脱A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预计敌人开始攻击的时间只剩下0004了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不行  要拖到最后一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人部队有反应了  是大型鱼雷！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:58.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arios  Cherudim  Seravee开始启动TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.11,0:17:00.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解  TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.22,0:17:07.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Field最大程度展开  托勒密紧急上浮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.41,0:17:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮向爆炸点的上方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.01,0:17:11.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想击中！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.73,0:17:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密转为飞行模式！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.05,0:17:32.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌舰从海面急速上浮  还在上升！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.45,0:17:34.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他  他们是真的想突破大气层吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:39.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我的预测还要早  是利用Trilobite的攻击为初期加速了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.04,0:17:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计算出敌舰的上升路线
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:49.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这  这种速度
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:50.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是舰船的速度吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.27,0:17:53.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了…了解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.01,0:18:00.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没用啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.46,0:18:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有炮口全部打开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.42,0:18:04.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,齐射！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.98,0:18:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:12.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别逃  Celestial Being！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是何等大胆的战术  看来果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.02,0:18:26.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌舰前行路线出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.02,0:18:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李拜巴尔上尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:35.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只需要将其上升角度改变3度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对Gadessa来说易如反掌！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.27,0:18:45.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直击？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.55,0:18:46.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.62,0:18:50.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高度突破六百千米了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.05,0:18:52.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就照这样脱离大气层
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.87,0:18:57.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,角度被改变了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.64,0:19:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的指挥官实在有一手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.94,0:19:05.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战的第一序列结束  敌人的TRANS-AM有时间限制
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.26,0:19:09.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就看杰江中校的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.35,0:19:15.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密现在高度一万千米  已越过低轨道环了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敌人部队的攻击！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.83,0:19:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道被埋伏了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.39,0:19:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM即将突破时限
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:26.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再启动之前GN Field将消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船体上部中弹！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.13,0:19:32.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人数量多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.16,0:19:36.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方  收容舰一艘  MS六台
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.26,0:19:37.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在预测范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.83,0:19:45.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的粒子用完了  一口气击溃他们！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.42,0:19:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:52.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人MS接近！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:19:59.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援军？不  那台机体不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:04.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是在脱离大气层的时候紧急放出来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.73,0:20:07.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一鼓作气瞄准主舰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.16,0:20:12.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OO  驱逐目标！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.38,0:20:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击沉敌舰了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.84,0:20:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方剩下的四台MS也撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:28.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预测很准确啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.89,0:20:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算逃出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.91,0:20:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐  从敌方MS上发来了可视信息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.44,0:20:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信息？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.86,0:20:44.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:45.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我读出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.16,0:20:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,读吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.16,0:20:52.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「谨向Celestial Being的丽莎·九条的战术致以敬意」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.96,0:20:57.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「在下是独立治安维持部队上校  卡蒂·马内金」  就这些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.27,0:20:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这信息怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.36,0:21:01.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马内金…
