Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.32,0:21:18.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.31,0:21:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是逃避不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.19,0:21:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法逃避那可憎的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.82,0:21:32.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那无法拭去的过去
